Class AirlineFilter

  • java.lang.Object
    • seng202.group6.model.Filter<Airline>
      • seng202.group6.model.AirlineFilter

  • public class AirlineFilter
extends Filter<Airline>
    Holds a set of conditions that can be compared against Airlines, and the methods to do so.
